**Benefits:**

* Reduced risk through targeted, small-scale changes
* Faster time-to-value with incremental improvements
* Improved maintainability by breaking down complex systems into smaller components

By following this approach, we can incrementally improve our legacy system while minimizing disruption and ensuring its stability and security over time.
